lodge the only place to rent a room in the 1300squaremile park 
we havent done anything special to promote the park but i 
believe there is much more awareness of the everglades and the 
parks environmental significance czarny said monday 
the last time the park attracted 1 million visitors in a year was 
in 1978 visitation decreased to a 1983 low of 500000 and has 
steadily climbed since 
