american countries to congressional legislation the life history of 
a potential defector the precise distribution of sandinista forces 
at a particular time among various villages gesell said listing 
the type of secrets north proposed to disclose 
this is a case charging fraud and deceit on the united states 
its chief executive and congress involving the use of arms profits 
in a manner allegedly unauthorized by the president the judge 
said it must remain focused on these issues rather than be 
derailed by the myriad unrelated issues raised by north 
