upgrade sewage treatment plants 
remove toxins from industrial waste water 
promote recycling 
control runoff from fertilizer pesticides and other chemicals 
expand research on water quality 
increase coast guard surveillance to prevent ocean dumping 
aggressively enforce existing antipollution laws 
edwards said a top priority was ending sewage overflow or the 
