accept the recommendation fazio said 
when the issue last arose two years ago the commission 
recommended an increase to 135000 which reagan in his budget cut 
to 89500 the senate passed a resolution rejecting even the 
reaganmodified increase but the house delayed its vote until it 
was too late to stop it 
