his right to address the world body in geneva after the united 
states denied him a visa preventing him from speaking at un 
headquarters in new york 
he also thanked the countries of western europe and japan for 
their recent stand following the palestine liberation organizations 
declaration of independence in algiers 
in israel radio reports had said that after arafats speech the 
