tucson ariz where they will be destroyed 
the european repair facility at gosslies 10 miles north of 
florennes is expected to operate until nearly all missiles covered 
by the treaty are removed 
the 21foot weapons are jetpropelled winged missiles with 
advanced guidance systems 
