computer firm failed to disclose the extent of the relationship 
between brooke partners lp and drexel burnham lambert inc and 
between lebow and drexel in advising and financing the deal 
the judge also said mai basic concealed information concerning 
past violations or alleged violations of federal securities laws by 
lebow and william weksel another principal in the bid 
mazzones injunction would halt the bid until the additional 
disclosures are made but the injunction is on hold until mai basic 
appeals to the 1st us circuit court of appeals in boston 
